        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> > (1 comment)\n > \n > Where is it used in the chart?\n\nThe 30220 port is used in kubernetes/portal/charts/portal-mariadb/values.yaml. My understanding is that AAI have to expose that external port in their file - kubernetes/aai/charts/aai-sparky-be/values.yaml.",
