        "timestamp": "2018-06-27 14:40:38.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> > > (1 comment)\n > >\n > > Where is it used in the chart?\n > \n > The 30220 port is used in kubernetes/portal/charts/portal-mariadb/values.yaml.\n > My understanding is that AAI have to expose that external port in\n > their file - kubernetes/aai/charts/aai-sparky-be/values.yaml.\n\nThe port is exposed using internalPort in services.yaml externalPort is not used in this chart.\nYou can do kubectl get svc --all-namespaces | grep spark and observe the service.",
